A simple calculator GUI. 

Capable of performing one of four arithmetic operations: addition, 
subtraction, multiplication, and division.

Uses infix notation (e.g. the sum of 2 and 2 would be computed by clicking
the button labelled "2", then the "+" button, and then "2" again, followed
by the "=" button. In more general form, 

    FIRST_OPERAND  OPERATOR  SECOND_OPERAND  EQUALS

Does not support operations entailing more than one operator or more than
two operands.
